.SH NAME
.P
japokwm - tiling made easy
.P
.SH SYNOPSIS
.P
\fBjapokwm\fR [options.\&.\&.\&] [command]
.P
.SH OPTIONS
.P
\fB-h, --help\fR
.RS 4
